5 (8) The task force shall report its findings and recommendations to the economic affairs interim
6 committee and the legislative council by July 1, 2026.
7
8 NEW SECTION. Section 2. Effective date. [This act] is effective on passage and approval.
9
10 NEW SECTION. Section 3. Termination. [Section 1] terminates December 31, 2026.
